Interface CommandSender

All Superinterfaces:
Audience, Identified, Pointered, Taggable, TagReadable, TagWritable
All Known Implementing Classes:
ConsoleSender, Player, ServerSender
public interface CommandSender extends Audience, Taggable, Identified
Represents something which can send commands to the server.

Main implementations are Player and ConsoleSender.
